divs: Sighting DetailsI was watering some plants around 7:45 pm I looked over my shoulder to see a light in the sky moving...it did not look like a plane but what really got my attention was the smaller object travelling somewhat in front of it...it was a smaller starlike object. They were fairly low and made no noise. They did not warble but were in perfect alignment and moved with ease and purpose very slowly until out of sight. Here is a spliced together video clip made from 3 short videos I was able to get...sorry about the quality my camera will not let me focus or view through the eyepiece when in record mode and it gives me a lot of trouble with less than stellar results. I'd like to say I see a lot of weird things in the sky around here. I don't know what these are but thought it was odd enough to report.
